30|$|In recent investigations, we {{discovered}} three undescribed species of Neenchelys from {{the waters of}} southern Taiwan, {{one of which is}} presumably a midwater species and the others are presumably <b>demersal</b> <b>species.</b> The addition of three new species described herein brings the total number of species in Neenchelys to nine.|$|R
